"I don't know what's happening.

105
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:08,631
"I don't trust myself when I'm in love.

106
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:10,631
"I get nervous. I say the wrong things.

107
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:14,508
