121
00:11:48,560 --> 00:11:51,870
"Or saying things like 'Think it will rain? '

122
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,393
"And I say 'I have no idea'

123
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:55,114
"and she says 'oh'

124
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:58,829
