at the California-blue sky.

125
00:11:58,920 --> 00:12:02,117
"That makes me thank God it's you, darling.

126
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,997
"This time it's your turn."

127
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,589
How are you?

128
00:12:17,680 --> 00:12:19,671
You look good. You seem happy.

129
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,428
