I was at Cecile's.

140
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:17,951
I forgot my phone charger.

141
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:20,232
Call her and check.

142
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,713
I'm going to bed.

143
