Is that it?

156
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:36,479
Proud of yourself?

157
00:17:38,920 --> 00:17:40,433
Are you proud?

158
00:17:41,360 --> 00:17:43,316
That's what you wanted, right?

159
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:46,117
- Right?
- You're drunk!

160
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,599
I'm not drunk.

161
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:50,032
Believe I'm drunk, if you want.

162
00:17:50,560 --> 00:17:52,710
But I can drink litres and not get drunk.

163
00:17:52,800 --> 00:17:54,313
For us, I won't be drunk.

164
00:17:55,040 --> 00:17:57,634
- I have all my wits about me.
- Good for you!

165
00:17:57,720 --> 00:18:01,349
I know it, I do. You know nothing!

166
