187
00:19:38,800 --> 00:19:40,711
That's the difference between us.

188
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:46,358
How can you know I love you?
How can you be sure?

189
00:19:47,920 --> 00:19:52,391
In the beginning,
before I followed you into this hole...

190
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:56,314
Our first days, I lulled myself to sleep
repeating "Paul loves me".

191
00:20:00,320 --> 00:20:03,630
I said it out loud, hundreds of times,
like a prayer.

192
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:07,395
Meaningless words.
We hardly knew each other.

193
00:20:07,480 --> 00:20:11,075
But something came about,
something was established.

194
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:15,358
