203
00:22:50,160 --> 00:22:54,870
Healthy, refreshing sleep happens
before midnight.

204
00:22:54,960 --> 00:22:57,030
Know what time you went to bed?

205
00:22:58,440 --> 00:23:01,398
No, please! I can't stand that.

206
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:02,913
Can't stand what?

207
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:06,913
I hope you don't stay up counting the minutes
till I get home!

208
00:23:08,800 --> 00:23:10,836
No one's counting minutes.

209
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:12,114
Smart-ass!

210
00:23:26,800 --> 00:23:27,915
Dad!

211
00:23:29,040 --> 00:23:30,871
- You're staying?
- Just ignore me.

212
00:23:30,960 --> 00:23:32,837
