The living room is my space!

216
00:23:44,080 --> 00:23:46,878
- We'll put the TV in your room.
- Don't move it.

217
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:47,949
Dad!

218
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:53,636
Did you speak to your brother today?

219
00:23:54,240 --> 00:23:56,196
How? You're talking crazy!

220
00:23:56,880 --> 00:23:58,279
Lower your voice.

221
00:24:00,040 --> 00:24:03,999
I couldn't possibly have talked to him.
I got home late, as you know.

222
00:24:06,120 --> 00:24:08,873
You promised me you'd talk to him.

223
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:13,439
Don't be selfish, Jonathan.
I hate that attitude.

224
00:24:13,520 --> 00:24:16,432
I couldn't talk to him! I just told you.

225
00:24:28,400 --> 00:24:30,834
Paul doesn't even want to talk to us.

226
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:36,589
Come on, Dad. I want to sleep.

227
00:24:38,360 --> 00:24:40,669
I'm asking you nicely to go away.

228
00:24:40,760 --> 00:24:42,557
You'll set the bed on fire!

229
00:24:42,640 --> 00:24:43,993
Go away!

230
00:24:46,120 --> 00:24:48,190
- Do you have class today?
- Yes.

231
00:24:48,280 --> 00:24:49,918
- What time?
- At noon.

232
00:24:52,120 --> 00:24:54,998
Then you'll help me with grocery shopping.

233
00:24:55,080 --> 00:24:57,230
Tomorrow's Saturday. Too many people.

234
00:24:57,320 --> 00:24:59,117
Yeah, we'll see.

235
00:24:59,200 --> 00:25:00,474
Now I'm sleeping.

236
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:03,312
I called your mother

237
