I'd better call the dentist for you.

250
00:25:51,680 --> 00:25:54,592
Must be something stuck in there.
Let me see.

251
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:56,910
Open your mouth. Open!

252
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:59,798
Go away! Leave me alone!
Go away, go!

253
00:26:02,480 --> 00:26:06,837
I'll go only when you tell me
what you'll do for your brother?

254
00:26:10,160 --> 00:26:13,311
I'm going to let him live out
his depression in peace.

255
00:26:13,400 --> 00:26:14,958
Very funny.

256
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:19,073
I'll fight to stop you from ruining everything.

257
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:24,037
You're incapable of feeling
the slightest pity for anyone.

258
00:26:24,120 --> 00:26:25,473
Not even your brother.

259
00:26:28,320 --> 00:26:30,515
You want me to pity Paul?

